{"issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/5345", "repo": "rails", "body": "`slice` suggests that this object is a `Hash`, so users will start expecting other `Enumerable` methods to be supported (reasonably IMO).\r\n\r\nIf you're going to treat an AR model as a `Hash`, it should go all in: `include Enumerable`, implement `each` to iterate over attributes, add a declaration to \"register\" methods whose names/values should be added to the attributes Hash in `each`.\r\n\r\nOtherwise I'd find a different name.", "_id": {"$oid": "5238198abd3543c15100e1a1"}, "issue_id": 5345, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/4439039", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/5345#issuecomment-4439039", "updated_at": "2012-03-11T13:37:41Z", "user": {"subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dchelimsky/subscriptions", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dchelimsky/events{/privacy}", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dchelimsky/repos", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dchelimsky/gists{/gist_id}", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/dchelimsky", "login": "dchelimsky", "gravatar_id": "5d38ab152e1e3e219512a9859fcd93af", "html_url": "https://github.com/dchelimsky", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dchelimsky/following{/other_user}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dchelimsky/received_events", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dchelimsky/orgs", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/5d38ab152e1e3e219512a9859fcd93af?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F46072631582fc240dd2674a7d063b040.png", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dchelimsky/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "id": 1075, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dchelimsky/followers", "type": "User"}, "created_at": "2012-03-11T13:37:41Z", "id": 4439039, "owner": "rails"}
